      "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:2:40:2",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/2/40/203",
      "text": [
        "أَمَّا بَعْدُ، فَقَدْ بَلَغَنِي عَنْكَ أَمْرٌ، إِنْ كُنْتَ فَعَلْتَهُ فَقَدْ أَسْخَطْتَ رَبَّكَ، وَعَصَيْتَ إِمَامَكَ، وَأَخْزَيْتَ أَمَانَتَكَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "Now, I have come to know such a thing about you that if you have done so then you have displeased your Lord, disobeyed your Imām and betrayed your trust."
        ]
      }
    },
    "verse_translations": [
      "en.sayed-ali-raza"
    ]
